text: Bugor () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Sasykolsky Selsoviet, Kharabalinsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 303 as of 2010. There are 9 streets. == Geography == It is located 27 km north-west from Kharabali. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kharabalinsky District
title: Bugor
